			<div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField14_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField14__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" ></div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-6">
			<div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField15_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField15__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" ></div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField16_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField16__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" ><hr /><h2>Policies<br></h2><div class="ms-rtestate-read ms-rte-wpbox"><div class="ms-rtestate-notify  ms-rtestate-read abea4936-03e0-4554-965b-cef2da608ccf" id="div_abea4936-03e0-4554-965b-cef2da608ccf" unselectable="on"><div id="MSOZoneCell_WebPartWPQ1" class="s4-wpcell-plain ms-webpartzone-cell ms-webpart-cell-vertical ms-fullWidth ">
	<div class="ms-webpart-chrome ms-webpart-chrome-vertical ms-webpart-chrome-fullWidth ">
	<div    id="WebPartWPQ1"  class="ms-WPBody "   style="" ><div id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl40_g_abea4936_03e0_4554_965b_cef2da608ccf">
		<div id="b8a7ed56-a564-49ea-85ea-2b374ed4d9c2">
			<accordion-search params="searchId: &#39;search_accordion-ctl00_ctl00_ctl40_g_abea4936_03e0_4554_965b_cef2da608ccf_ctl01&#39;">

			</accordion-search>
		</div><script type="text/javascript">
			ko.applyBindings(null, document.getElementById('b8a7ed56-a564-49ea-85ea-2b374ed4d9c2'))
		</script><div class="list-unstyled panel-group or-accordion-list" id="accordion-ctl00_ctl00_ctl40_g_abea4936_03e0_4554_965b_cef2da608ccf_ctl01">
			<div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-b0125731-45e0-42be-a52a-4de85f38b1e9">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#b0125731-45e0-42be-a52a-4de85f38b1e9" aria-controls="b0125731-45e0-42be-a52a-4de85f38b1e9" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="7ae95356-63d6-4305-a70b-7dd5a562f554">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Benefits counseling</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="b0125731-45e0-42be-a52a-4de85f38b1e9" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass167D2226B0CC41AB9FBDE1CB3644F457"><p>​Benefits and Work Incentive Counseling services help people with disabilities make informed decisions about work, benefits and the use of work incentives to achieve their employment goals.</p><p><strong>Policy Documents and Related Infor​mation</strong></p><ul><li>
               <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/benefits-counseling-referral-process.PDF" title="Helpful flow chart for referral process">Benefits Counseling Referral Process Flow Chart</a></li><li>
               <a href="https&#58;//youtu.be/5deIFQAAgi0" title="Informational video on maximizing your work hours and still receive benefits.">Maximizing Hours Video</a></li><li>
               <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/odds-approved-benefits-counselors.pdf">ODDS Approved Benefits Counselors</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/ef-odds-win-certification.pdf">ODDS WIN Certification Program​</a><br></li><li>
               <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/win/Pages/default.aspx#quickreference" title="Browse through helpful information regarding working and SSDI or SSI. Information regarding medicare, medicade and more.">SSD​I and SSI Employment Information and Resources</a></li><li>
               <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-benefits-counseling.pdf" title="Read outlined requirements related to benefits counseling">Worker Guide&#58; ODDS Benefits Counseling</a><br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-3aeaf0ff-f1ec-4c2f-881c-c9df1fa50003">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#3aeaf0ff-f1ec-4c2f-881c-c9df1fa50003" aria-controls="3aeaf0ff-f1ec-4c2f-881c-c9df1fa50003" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="2bd18cf6-57d1-4b8c-988b-b2cd4e290445">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Career Development Plan (CDP)</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="3aeaf0ff-f1ec-4c2f-881c-c9df1fa50003" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassCCE544418B034CEAB581CC1805F78234"><p>​The Career Development Plan (CDP) identifies the individual's employment goals and objectives. The CDP is based on person-centered planning principles.<br></p><p> 
      <strong>Policy Documents and Related​ Information</strong></p><ul><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/employment-discussion-guide.pdf" title="An introduction to conversation and discussions">Employment Discussion Guide and​ Selecting Employment Providers”</a>​<br></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/osac-employment-guide.pdf" title="Learn how employment can work for you.">OSAC Guide to Community Employment</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/employment-qa-questions-2025-2027.pdf">Quality Assurance Review Questions 2025-2027​</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="https&#58;//sharedsystems.dhsoha.state.or.us/DHSForms/Served/de0684.pdf">Workers Guide&#58; OSAC Transition from ​School to Work</a></li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-competitive-integrated-employment-requirements.pdf">Workers Guide&#58; Competitive Integrated Employment​</a><br></li></ul><p><strong>Worker's Guides​</strong></p><ul><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/career-development-planning-guide.pdf">​Career Development Plan​ (CDP) Guide</a> - Updated 2024<br></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/not-to-explore-employment-guide.pdf">Decision Not to Explore Employment (DNE) Guide</a> - Updated 2024<br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-e81ac685-addf-4a77-8488-457e618fd599">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#e81ac685-addf-4a77-8488-457e618fd599" aria-controls="e81ac685-addf-4a77-8488-457e618fd599" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="3521e5e9-eec2-4143-ba61-1b68fbbae92e">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Competitive integrated employment</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="e81ac685-addf-4a77-8488-457e618fd599" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassE63520E36AE645FD87EF306B09C1D279"><p>Competitive Integrated Employment is full or part-time work at minimum wage or higher, with wages and benefits similar to those without disabilities performing the same work, and fully integrated with co-workers without disabilities.</p><p>
      <strong>Policy documents and related​ information</strong>​ </p><ul><li>
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/vr/Documents/competitive-integrated-employment-toolkit.pdf" title="Use when determining whether a specific  job is Competitive Integrated Employment">Competitive Integrated Employme​nt Toolkit​</a></li><li><a href="https&#58;//secure.sos.state.or.us/oard/viewSingleRule.action?ruleVrsnRsn=263229" title="External link to Secretary of State Oregon Administrative Rules">OAR 582-001 Definition for Competitive Employment</a></li><li><a href="/odhs/rules-policy/oddsrulesdocs/411-345.pdf">OAR 411-435 on Employment Services to Individuals with I/DD</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/job-coaching-without-vr-placement-form.docx">Job Coaching Without Vocational Rehabilitation Placement​​ Form</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/vr-dd-service-crosswalk-presentation.pdf">Vocational Rehabilitation and ODDS Service Crosswalk PowerPoint</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/vr/Documents/oregon-vr-policy-manual.pdf">Vocational Rehabilitation Policy Manual​</a><br></li><li><a href="https&#58;//rsa.ed.gov/sites/default/files/subregulatory/RSA-FAQ-22-02.docx">FAQ&#58; Rehabilitation Services Administration definition of Competitive Integrated Employment​</a>&#160;</li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-employment-table-contents.pdf">Worker Guide&#58; ODDS Employment Services Table of Contents​</a></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-employment-stabilization.pdf">Worker Guide&#58; ODDS Employment Stabilization</a></li></ul><p> 
      <strong> Transmitt​als </strong></p><p></p><ul><li>​<a href="/odhs/transmittals/oddstransmittals/im20001.pdf" title="Competitive Integrated Employment&#58; ODDS and VR guidance on requirements for employment services ">Competitive Integrated Employment&#58; ODDS and VR guidance on requirements for employment services​</a>&#160;</li><li><a href="/odhs/transmittals/oddstransmittals/pt15017.pdf" title="Wage Requirements for ODDS Employment Services">Wage Requirements for ODDS Employment Services​</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/vr-ar-20-01-competitive-integrated-employment-toolkit.pdf">Release of WIOA Competitive Integrated Employment Toolkit&#160;</a><br></li></ul><p></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-8f279576-9af7-4363-b7e2-fb79b4b38f4b">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#8f279576-9af7-4363-b7e2-fb79b4b38f4b" aria-controls="8f279576-9af7-4363-b7e2-fb79b4b38f4b" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="00b41f19-8ba0-41f2-ba49-c2c8939a9dd2">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Core competencies/training requirements</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="8f279576-9af7-4363-b7e2-fb79b4b38f4b" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassCDBC1D6E508D401384700E149D81D97C"><p>ODDS and VR are committed to contracting employment services from qualified Employment Professionals who meet training and competencies adopted by Oregon Employment First.</p><p> 
      <strong>Policy documents and related​ information</strong></p><ul><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/core-competency-contingency-form.docx" title="This form should only be used if the system is temporarily unavailable due to a technical problem or other issue. ">Core Competency Checklist - Fillable</a></li><li title="A basic introduction to supported employment for Employment Professionals">
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/odds-employment-core-competencies.pdf">Core Competencies - Slide deck​</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/Documents/department-approved-employment-service-provider-training-courses.pdf">Department Approved Training Courses​</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/provider-training-requirement.pdf" title="Training Requirements for Office of Developmental Disabilities Services (ODDS)’ Employment Services Providers">Providers Training Requirements</a></li><li>
         <a href="https&#58;//survey.alchemer.com/s3/6464966/Oregon-Office-of-Developmental-Disabilities-Non-residential-Provider-Assessment" title="Provider required assessment for delivering non-residential ODDS and Medicaid-funded Home and Community Based Services (HCBS). ">Provider Site Assessment</a>&#160;​</li><li>​<a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-ef-core-comp-trainings.pdf" title="Outline of the training requirements and quick access to the Core Competency modules">Worker Guide&#58; Employment Core Competency Trainings</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-employment-professional-qualifications-training.pdf" title="Training requirements as outlined in OAR 411-345">Worker Guide&#58; Employment Professional Qualifications and Training</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-request-continuing-ed-hours-employment-professionals.pdf">Worker ​Guide&#58; Employment Training and Conference CE Approval</a></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-employment-services-supported-employment-curriculum.pdf">Worker Guide&#58; Certification for Supported Employment Curriculum​</a>&#160;</li></ul><p> 
      <strong>Transm​ittals</strong></p><ul><li>
         <a href="/odhs/transmittals/oddstransmittals/im20002.pdf">Updated Department Approved Continuing Education Credit Training List​</a></li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/employment-professional-qualifications-training.pdf">Updated Employment Professional Qualifications and Training Worker's Guide​​</a></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-679d1926-d5c7-410f-a9e9-e27c489bfb64">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#679d1926-d5c7-410f-a9e9-e27c489bfb64" aria-controls="679d1926-d5c7-410f-a9e9-e27c489bfb64" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="ad1a757e-1e68-47eb-b17b-b70585704d95">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Discovery</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="679d1926-d5c7-410f-a9e9-e27c489bfb64" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassED4A65B9890E445382FFF88AB5E961A3"><p>​This is a person-centered, time-limited, employment planning service. It can help an individual obtain, maintain, or advance in a competitive integrate​d job at or above minimum wage. Activities in the service can vary and can identify an individual's interests, strengths, and abilities.<br></p><p> 
      <strong>Policy Documents and Relate​​d Information - Effective 9/1/2​​021</strong></p><ul><li>
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/discovery-profile.pdf">Discovery Profile</a><br></li><ul><li><a href="/odhs/Documents/troubleshooting-opening-forms.pdf">​Troubleshooting Guide for Discovery Profile Form​</a><br></li></ul><li>
         <a href="/odhs/transmittals/oddstransmittals/21070.pdf">Virtual Discovery Cha​nges​</a></li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-discovery-guidelines.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58;&#160;Discovery Guidelines for SCs PAs and Providers&#160;</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/discovery-employment-tour-prompts.docx">Discovery Employment Tour Prompts and Ideas</a></li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/discovery-sample-home-visit-questions.pdf">Discovery Home Visit Sample Questions</a><br></li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/pre-discovery-checklist.docx">Pre-Discovery Checklist</a></li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-discovery-experiential-components.pdf">Discovery Experiential Components Worker Guide</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-workers-comp-insurance-coverage.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58; Worker Compensation Insurance Coverage</a></li><li>
         <a href="https&#58;//youtu.be/peNAySsTrDg">Video - Discovery​</a><br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-988f5701-8ebd-4fe1-a57c-444f068f19d9">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#988f5701-8ebd-4fe1-a57c-444f068f19d9" aria-controls="988f5701-8ebd-4fe1-a57c-444f068f19d9" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="b10fc061-53c8-4df5-a093-3278f307fb45">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Employment Outcomes System (EOS)</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="988f5701-8ebd-4fe1-a57c-444f068f19d9" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass310A17FEC5814F33A34DF7DF0FF4E229"><p>The&#160;<a href="https&#58;//eos.oregon.gov/">Employment Outcomes System (EOS)​</a> is a system for collecting semiannual data on the employment o​utcomes of adults with intellectual and/or developmental disabilities who are receiving employment services from​ ODDS. Job seekers can use this data to research employment providers in their area.<br></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-f44ef644-df41-4bef-a32a-6ebca01481c0">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#f44ef644-df41-4bef-a32a-6ebca01481c0" aria-controls="f44ef644-df41-4bef-a32a-6ebca01481c0" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="57c71f32-c00e-4ffd-bc6d-1f6c897901c2">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Employment path community</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="f44ef644-df41-4bef-a32a-6ebca01481c0" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass95DAB2DDBAD14604817FAC1F585AAE30">​<p>Employment Path Community Services should provide learning and work experiences. It may include volunteer opportunities. The goal of this service is for an individual to develop employment skills to be used in an integrated job.​​<br></p><p> 
      <strong>Policy Documents and Related​ Information</strong>​</p><ul><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-1-on1-employment.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58; One to One “Solo” Employment Path Services</a></li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-workers-comp-insurance-coverage.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58; Worker Compensation Insurance Coverage</a>	</li><li>
         <a href="/odhs/idd/employmentservicesfactsheets/factsheet-employment-path-en.pdf">Fact Sheet - Employment Path Community​</a>	</li><li> 
         <a href="https&#58;//youtu.be/4DWebPItUug">Video - Employment Path Community​</a><br></li></ul>
<p>As of September 2020, ODDS no longer funds sheltered workshop services.</p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-395f7ca9-15ea-4376-b6c7-4deab5ade8d9">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#395f7ca9-15ea-4376-b6c7-4deab5ade8d9" aria-controls="395f7ca9-15ea-4376-b6c7-4deab5ade8d9" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="6bd18063-9ea0-4403-83ee-a743f9f44c7b">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Employment stabilization and competitive integrated employment</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="395f7ca9-15ea-4376-b6c7-4deab5ade8d9" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass6DEA0386895B4820981F12C3C4B665EC"><p>​The Employment Stabilization Worker's Guide outlines the process related to transfers from VR-funded job coaching to ODDS-funded job coaching. It also specifies how and when ODDS can fund job coaching in its entirety.<br></p><p>   <strong>Policy Documents and Related​ Information</strong></p><ul><li>
      <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/vr-dd-service-crosswalk-presentation.pdf">Vocational Rehabilitation and ODDS Service Crosswalk PowerPoint</a><br></li><li>
      <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/job-coaching-without-vr-placement-form.docx">Job Coaching Without Vocational Rehabilitation Placement​​ Form</a></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-employment-stabilization.pdf">Worker's Guide - Employment Stabilization</a><br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-c9c9ab0e-d695-40a2-958d-ce234c10f7d4">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#c9c9ab0e-d695-40a2-958d-ce234c10f7d4" aria-controls="c9c9ab0e-d695-40a2-958d-ce234c10f7d4" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="d2a5505f-16dc-4266-a70e-0d214a40da23">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Home and community-based services (HCBS)</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="c9c9ab0e-d695-40a2-958d-ce234c10f7d4" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass8FF9CBEC22AB46309AECDFCECF944C07"><p>​ODDS services are funded through the 
      <a href="https&#58;//www.medicaid.gov/medicaid/hcbs/index.html">Medicaid Home and Community Based Services (HCBS) program​</a>. New federal regulations specify that all HCBS services must be offered in integrated community settings. Those settings that do not comply have time to transition and come into compliance, as outlined in the state level transition plan and provider level transition plans.</p><p>
      <strong>Policy Documents and Rela​ted Information</strong></p><ul><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/hcbsdocs/oregon-approved-transition-plan.pdf">Oregon HCBS Transition Plan​</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/Pages/hcbs.aspx">ODHS HCBS webpage</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/hcbsdocs/odds-employment-services-onsite-review-checklist.pdf" title="Checklist Tool for Employment Service Settings">Tools for Onsite Reviews - Employment Service Setting</a>	</li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/hcbsdocs/hsd-self-assessment.docx">HCBS Provider Self-Assessment</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/hcbsdocs/odds-onsite-assessment-non-res-day-services.pdf" title="Checklist Tool for Non-Residential Day Service Settings">Tools for Onsite Reviews - Day Service Settings</a>​<br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-453e8351-eca8-4cbd-8ea6-8b609fccd2f1">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#453e8351-eca8-4cbd-8ea6-8b609fccd2f1" aria-controls="453e8351-eca8-4cbd-8ea6-8b609fccd2f1" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="8d34365c-6923-4daa-9f2b-e8c802d604d5">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Independent contractors</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="453e8351-eca8-4cbd-8ea6-8b609fccd2f1" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassB2F78236DCB141A9ABDEDB7498EAA388"><p><br><br></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-3d992e64-d810-47a1-b230-a25eeb1c7fc5">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#3d992e64-d810-47a1-b230-a25eeb1c7fc5" aria-controls="3d992e64-d810-47a1-b230-a25eeb1c7fc5" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="27e77769-7653-4714-ae00-49d4f31c67c4">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Job coaching</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="3d992e64-d810-47a1-b230-a25eeb1c7fc5" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass2137C25DBC5A43ECB79362AC16DDE21C"><p>Job Coaching is a support service for an individual to maintain or advance in an individual job in a competitive integrated employment setting in the general workforce, including customized employment or self-employment.</p><p>
      <strong>Policy Documents and Related​ Information</strong></p><ul><li>
         <a href="https&#58;//youtu.be/1uOq7cWKrOc">Becoming a PSW Job Coach - Video​</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/idd/employmentservicesfactsheets/factsheet-job-coaching-en.pdf">Job Coaching - Fact Sheet</a></li><li> 
         <a href="https&#58;//youtu.be/7KcfFBTbH5U">How Job Coaching C​an Benefit You​ - Video</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/ef-fading-presentation.pdf">Job Coaching - Fading Presentation</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-job-coaching.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58; Job Coaching</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-job-coaching-without-vr.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58; ODDS Job Coaching Without Vocational Rehabilitation</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-retention-payments-job-placement.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58; ODDS Retention Payments</a>	</li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-employment-table-contents.pdf">Worker's&#160;Guide&#58; ODDS Employment Services Table of Contents</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/Documents/odds-expenditure-guidelines.pdf">ODDS Expenditure Guidelines</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-psw-employment-services-enrollment.pdf">Personal Support Worker Employment Services Enrollment</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="https&#58;//sharedsystems.dhsoha.state.or.us/DHSForms/Served/de2710.pdf">Personal Support Worker Job Coach Brochure</a><br></li><li> 
         <a href="https&#58;//sharedsystems.dhsoha.state.or.us/DHSForms/Served/de9477.pdf" title="Find out what a job coach does">How to become ​a Personal Support Worker Job Coach</a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/factsheet-job-coaching-direct-contact.pdf" title="Fact sheet&#58; ODDS Job Coaching Payment Methodology and Entering Direct Contact Time">​Fact sheet&#58; ODDS Job Coaching Payment Methodology and Entering Direct Contact Time</a></li></ul><p>
      <strong>Forms</strong></p><ul><li>​ 
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/job-coaching-without-vr-placement-form.docx">Job Coaching Without Vocational Rehabilitation Placement​​ Form</a></li><li>​ 
         <a href="/odhs/idd/Documents/maintenance-job-coaching-request-form.docx">Maintenance Job Coaching Request​ Form</a><br></li></ul><div><strong>Rates</strong><br></div><div><ul><li><a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/job-coaching-proposed-rate-models.pdf">ODDS Job Coaching Rate Model effective July 1, 2026</a></li><li><a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/job-coaching-rate-change-faq.pdf">Job Coaching rate change Frequently Asked Questions​</a><br></li></ul></div><p>
      <strong>Transm​ittals</strong></p><ul><li>​<a href="/odhs/transmittals/oddstransmittals/ar20063.pdf" title="Stipend Payments for PSWs with Job Coach Specialty">Stipend Payments for PSWs with Job Coach Specialty​​​</a>&#160;​</li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-35f04171-4801-495f-9414-10ce68e3ce7b">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#35f04171-4801-495f-9414-10ce68e3ce7b" aria-controls="35f04171-4801-495f-9414-10ce68e3ce7b" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="cc18c72b-c706-42d9-9e95-f4d3bd0fe7bb">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Job development</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="35f04171-4801-495f-9414-10ce68e3ce7b" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassF4262F2828C14EE1AA46AEFDC54224F4"><p>​A Job Developer identifies job opportunities in the workplace where an individual's skills match the employer's need. Job Development may include support with the application and interview process, and visits with potential employers.</p><p>
      <strong>Policy Documents and Related​ Information</strong></p><ul><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/idd/employmentservicesfactsheets/factsheet-job-development-en.pdf">Job Development - Fact Sheet</a></li><li> 
         <a href="https&#58;//youtu.be/Eb4QTJ6PKgY">Job Development - Video​</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/wg-job-development-vr-order-of-selection.pdf">Worker's Guide&#58; ODDS Job Development During VR Order of Selection​</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/EngagementInnovation/sample-job-development-plan.docx">Sample ODDS Job Development Plan​</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/EngagementInnovation/sample-job-development-report.docx">Sample ODDS Job Development Monthly Report​</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/job-development-verification-form.docx">Required Job Development Verification Form​</a><br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-f564d8cc-4ac4-422b-993f-96805f849f7d">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#f564d8cc-4ac4-422b-993f-96805f849f7d" aria-controls="f564d8cc-4ac4-422b-993f-96805f849f7d" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="03908ac0-55d9-4005-a9a8-e1f9f5b7c54e">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Lane v. Brown settlement</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h3><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="f564d8cc-4ac4-422b-993f-96805f849f7d" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass313F77BF13F64DBBB08B971E7113C617"><p>​Lane v. Brown is a class action involving employment services that Oregon provides to people with intellectual and developmental disabilities (I/DD). A settlement was reached at the end of 2015, which was accepted and approved by the Oregon Federal District Court in January 2016.​<br></p><p>    
         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Pages/publications.aspx#lb">View reports​</a>​​​</p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-0f85a7aa-1800-4279-bc4b-563d50f13b32">
				<h3>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#0f85a7aa-1800-4279-bc4b-563d50f13b32" aria-controls="0f85a7aa-1800-4279-bc4b-563d50f13b32" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="3c843d40-87d2-4041-b217-fe0440f8e951">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-thumb">
								<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.oregon.gov/odhs/PublishingImages/icons/arrow-green-192.png" alt="&quot;&quot;" />
							</div><div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Personal assistance and other related services</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
