         <a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/wg-sacu-employment-services.pdf">Employment Services while with the Stabilization and Crisis Unit (SACU) </a></li><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/workerguides/employment-dsa-ltccn-dns.pdf">Long-Term Care Community Nursing and Direct Nursing Services during employment or DSA services</a><br></li><li><a href="/odhs/employment-first/Documents/odds-otj-attendant-care.pdf">On the Job Attendant Care Powerpoint​</a>​<br></li><li> 
