						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass839677A9BE04445D9AFA27F48372F6F8"><p> 
      <strong>​Policy Documents and Rela​ted Information</strong></p><ul><li> 
         <a href="/odhs/providers-partners/idd/Documents/release-of-info-form-me3010.pdf" title="Statewide Release of Information Form - English">Release of Information Form 3010 English</a></li><li> 
         <a href="https&#58;//sharedsystems.dhsoha.state.or.us/DHSForms/Served/ms3010.pdf" title="Statewide Release of Information form - Spanish">Release of Information&#160;Form 3010 Spanish</a></li><li> 
